<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Habitica - About Me</title>
    <link href="css/bootstrap-5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        .bd-placeholder-img {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            text-anchor: middle;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -moz-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .bd-placeholder-img-lg {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
        }

        /* Custom color style */
        .text-custom {
            color: #4e89ae !important;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .bg-custom {
            background-color: #4e89ae !important;
        }

        .border-custom {
            border-color: #4e89ae !important;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            background-color: #4e89ae;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            background-color: #3a698f;
        }

        .btn-danger-custom {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn-danger-custom:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
        }

        .about-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .profile-pic {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 4px solid #fff;
        }

        .profile-info {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .profile-info strong {
            color: #ffeb3b;
        }

        .main {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e89ae, #56c5d0);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Navbar custom style */
        .navbar-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e89ae, #56c5d0);
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: #fff !important;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .nav-link.active {
            background-color: #3a698f !important;
            color: #fff !important;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e89ae, #56c5d0);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="css/headers.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-3 mb-4 border-bottom border-custom navbar-custom">
            <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto text-white text-decoration-none">
                <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32"><use xlink:href="#bootstrap"/></svg>
                <span class="fs-4">Welcome to Habitica, <%= fname %>!</span>
            </a>

            <ul class="nav nav-pills">
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="/habits" class="nav-link">My Habits</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="/about" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page">About</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="/logout" class="nav-link">Log Out</a></li>
            </ul>
        </header>
    </div>
    <div class="b-example-divider"></div>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="container about-section">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
            <img src="/img/profile-picture.jpg" alt="Profile Picture" class="profile-pic">
            <p class="profile-info">
                <strong>Name:</strong> Seifer Rija Boado<br>
                <strong>Email:</strong> seiferboado101@gmail.com<br>
                <strong>Occupation:</strong> BS-IT Graduate and Software Developer looking for a job<br>
            </p>
            <p>
                Welcome to my page! I'm Seifer, I am a passionate developer with a keen interest in building web applications that help improve productivity and well-being. Habitica is one of my favorite projects, and I'm excited to share it with you. When I'm not coding, I enjoy going to the gym, reading, and exploring new technologies.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        // Custom scripts can go here if needed
    </script>
</body>
</html>
